snippet.title: Is this Game Trying to Kill Me? Preface | Release trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2875280/Is_this_Game_Trying_to_Kill_Me_Preface/

This is a small free prequel to the Is this Game Trying to Kill Me?. An old cabin deep in the dense forest, a strange computer, and a game that's trying to kill you!
